{"tid":1851361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果，我有多一個口罩，你會不會跟我一起走？","createTime":"2020-01-30T04:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T05:03:24.000Z","uid":75964,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"754cda244d1827b8bca5007823d2afa565722fc1","tid":1851361,"uid":75964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不知道什麼時候開始，我變成一個很小心的人，每次我落街的時候，我都會戴口罩，你永遠都不會知道什麼時候沙士，什麼時候WARS。"},{"pid":"c9404ec7a86a3d38b262964348cf0a12e72e9142","tid":1851361,"uid":75964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:09:11.000Z","msg":"不知道從什麼時候開始，在什麼東西上面都有個日期，口罩會過期，眼罩會過期，連防毒面罩都會過期，我開始懷疑，在這個世界上，還有什麼東西是不會過期的？"},{"pid":"45685a1aff5d7bb1dc2777dcc0d42d0b91e640a6","tid":1851361,"uid":75964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"去2046的乘客都只有一個目地，就是找回失去的口罩。因為在2046，一切事物都無受到感染。沒有人知道這是不是真的，因為從來沒有人回來過。我是唯一的一個。"},{"pid":"680f6f929141dee0314e41f21b683f18a44cce00","tid":1851361,"uid":65378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"Tg me plz"},{"pid":"c356a2b3e35d1fe919093d993d9b6af935d7df99","tid":1851361,"uid":75964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"680f6f929141dee0314e41f21b683f18a44cce00","tid":1851361,"uid":65378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"Tg me plz"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:10:57.000Z","msg":"共享大灣區人榮耀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd14d1c9c6bc2a7f4bd8eb2b83d1edde7769c6b","tid":1851361,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家已經係獨立最佳時機，你，仲等緊啲咩<br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：種族清洗 <br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851323</a>"}